  <brief_title>China-Administration of Nicorandil Group（CHANGE）</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Nicorandil on Cardiac Infarct Size in Patients With ST-segment Elevation Acute Myocardial Infarction Undergoing Primary Percutaneous Coronary Intervention</official_title>
  <sponsors>
